OL,3,CBBC News' Clive Myrie apologises for
OL,4,Cnot declaring thousands earnt from
OL,5,Cevents
OL,7,FBBC News presenter Clive Myrie has
OL,8,Fapologised after he failed to declare
OL,9,Fthousands of pounds in payments
OL,10,Freceived from appearing at events
OL,11,Foutside of the BBC.
OL,13,FMyrie, 60, said the error was due to
OL,14,F"several administrative issues" and
OL,15,Fsaid he will not be taking part in
OL,16,Fpaid external events for the
OL,17,Fforeseeable future, except for some
OL,18,Fpre-existing commitments.
