OL,3,CBBC News' Clive Myrie apologises for
OL,4,Cnot declaring thousands earnt from
OL,5,Cevents
OL,7,FIn a post on X, he said: "An apology -
OL,8,FI've had several administrative
OL,9,Fissues, and I didn't fill out the
OL,10,Fcorrect paperwork for some of my
OL,11,Fexternal public events, so they
OL,12,Fhaven't been published until now.
OL,14,F"I've told the BBC I won't be taking
OL,15,Fpart in any more paid external events
OL,16,Fin the foreseeable future, beyond a
OL,17,Fhandful of pre-existing commitments,
OL,18,Fso that this doesn't happen again.
OL,20,F"My sincere apologies."
