OL,3,CBBC News' Clive Myrie apologises for
OL,4,Cnot declaring thousands earnt from
OL,5,Cevents
OL,7,FThe register was introduced in 2021
OL,8,Fand exists for on-air journalists and
OL,9,Fsenior staff members to declare
OL,10,Fexternal work which involves payment.
OL,12,FOn Wednesday, the BBC published the
OL,13,Fregister for the third quarter of
OL,14,F2024, noting that "a number of events
OL,15,Fthat were not submitted to the
OL,16,Fregister in previous quarters have
OL,17,Fbeen retrospectively published today".
