OL,3,CBBC News' Clive Myrie apologises for
OL,4,Cnot declaring thousands earnt from
OL,5,Cevents
OL,7,FThe corporation said the register is
OL,8,Fpart of its commitment to
OL,9,Fimpartiality, and those who have
OL,10,Ffailed to follow the correct process
OL,11,Fhave been reminded of their
OL,12,Fresponsibilities.
OL,14,FIn cases of non-compliance, "robust
OL,15,Fmanagement action" has been taken and
OL,16,Fthat disciplinary action can be taken
OL,17,Ffor breaches, the BBC added.
OL,19,FGuidelines outlining the number of
OL,20,Fpaid external events individuals can
OL,21,Fattend will be updated, the BBC added.
